high_descs: Turn right and go to the wall.  Turn right and face the table on the right side of it.
Pick up the credit card that is to the right of the glass vase.
With the credit card in hand move to face the same table but on the left side of it.
Place the credit card on the plate that is on the table.
Pick up the plate with the credit card on it.
With the plate in hand turn and go to the table that is next to the couch with the purple pillow on it.
Place the plate to the right of the lamp that is on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place plate and credit card on table next to couch.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the corner of the room.
Pick up the credit card on the shelf near the floor.
Take a step left.
Place the credit card on the white plate.
Pick up the white plate.
Turn right and walk straight towards the couch, and then go to the table to the left of the couch.
Place the plate on the black table to the right of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a credit card on it on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and move between the wall to the right and a table to the left and come to a shelf on the right.
Pick up a credit card from the shelf closest to the wall
Move slightly to the left of where the credit card was picked up from
Place the credit card on a plate just to the left in front of a tea pot
Pick up the white plate now holding the credit card from the cabinet
Turn to the right keeping the wall to the left and straight to a black side table
Place the plate with the card directly to the right of the lamp
anns.task_desc: Placing a plate with a credit card on it on a side table
